  "body": "# Bug Report\n\n## Problem\n\nWe had a mailserver outage recently whereby 2 mailservers (central-02 & central-03) were throwing errors upon request.\n\nThe system correctly swapped mailserver when it was happening, but it would keep re-selecting them as they had the best ping time for some users.\n\n#### Expected behavior\n\nMailservers that are not responding correctly are not re-selected for at least some period of time.\n\n#### Actual behavior\n\nMailserver kept being selected because the fastest in ping time.\n\n\n#### Notes\n\nWe should probably implement some cooldown timer where mailservers should not be re-selected if they are erroring.",
